&lt;li&gt;Serve as the primary liaison to work cross-functionally with clients, fund administrators, and business groups to manage and rectify data exceptions.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Collaborate with Product Managers to define and implement data projects for existing and new features and workflows.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Develop exception management tools to strengthen data quality control and produce metrics and dashboards to inform stakeholders on prioritizing resolutions.&lt;/li&gt;
