&lt;li&gt;Bachelor’s degree or higher in computer science, business analytics, business administration, finance or in a related field&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Proven track record of performing root cause analysis and coordinating with engineers on investigation and resolution&lt;/li&gt;
