&lt;li&gt;Strong knowledge of the Investment Company Act of 1940, the Investment Advisers Act of 1940, the Securities Act of 1933, the Securities Exchange Act of 1934, and FINRA regulations&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Working knowledge of Latin American fund offering rules and regulatory frameworks private funds and other products&lt;/li&gt;
