&lt;li&gt;Member in good standing of Florida Bar, another state or jurisdiction&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Law firm or in-house experience at an asset management firm or broker dealer is a plus&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong interpersonal and leadership skills&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Willingness to learn new topics and work in an evolving business environment&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Organized and detail-oriented with big picture capability&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
